Having a good heart isn’t weakness - it’s your superpower. En The world can be hard, cold, and fast. But don’t let that change who you are. Never regret being the one who smiles first, who forgives, who gives without expecting anything back. Being kind, even when others aren’t, takes courage.
A good heart often gets misunderstood, taken for granted, or hurt - but don’t let the world make you regret it. Because in the end, everything you put out into the Universe comes back to you multiplied. Kindness grows. Love expands. Compassion returns.
So even when you’re tired, keep choosing to be good. Keep showing up for others and for yourself. The energy you pour into the world doesn’t disappear - it finds its way back, sometimes in the most beautiful, unexpected forms. f
Hold your head high. Protect your peace. And keep your heart open.
